<a href="https://www.goodreads.com/book/show/239907.Queer_Theory"><img alt="Queer Theory: An Introduction" src="https://i.gr-assets.com/images/S/compressed.photo.goodreads.com/books/1386920059l/239907._SX98_.jpg" />
