<a href="https://www.goodreads.com/book/show/75405.In_a_Queer_Time_and_Place"><img alt="In a Queer Time and Place: Transgender Bodies, Subcultural Lives" src="https://i.gr-assets.com/images/S/compressed.photo.goodreads.com/books/1417981357l/75405._SX98_.jpg" />
